{"tid":306264,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人去親旅行, 屋企人都好煩?","createTime":"2017-07-02T11:22:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-03T00:27:34.000Z","uid":2924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"80e5d6487d69e291e29a4ad5d9fd7dc01a59f497","tid":306264,"uid":2924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T11:22:02.000Z","msg":"見D人個個月都飛, 點樣同屋企人講去旅行?<br />\n<br />\n我一年去幾次旅行, 同屋企人單一聲, 都煩到嘔, 好煩<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲打有同樣問題?"},{"pid":"642e6a4c1e07d0b4a4ebf6fcde8092424e853994","tid":306264,"uid":46615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T17:57:43.000Z","msg":"屋企人成日話去旅行係亂fing錢，話我唔識儲錢，淨係識玩，煩到嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a21b6ce0f454fcd6cb76127ef2018d0e1b39bcd","tid":306264,"uid":5131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T18:06:10.000Z","msg":"我都係 我今個月底去泰國玩幾日 仲未講比屋企人知 一陣佢地又話我唔草錢亂咁洗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  大佬 緊係趁後生去多啲地方嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"336d6f040eec8d2e887ea1224841067eefc4fb4a","tid":306264,"uid":12536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T18:06:56.000Z","msg":"我老豆都係咁<br />\n係都要我搵返佢後生果陣去過幾多旅行出黎俾佢聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔係用佢錢去"},{"pid":"475b138d2fd8061412a959647c6baf88bbbe8579","tid":306264,"uid":100623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T22:37:16.000Z","msg":"因為佢地覺得去一次旅行係要洗幾皮野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n實情我一年去3次都唔過2皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"267cdc3043c394e4d932b3aaf48f0eb0c41bbedd","tid":306264,"uid":1367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T00:27:34.000Z","msg":"原因有兩個<br />\n1/ 窮 ( 個個月五位數家用一定冇野講)<br />\n2/ 冇交帶 ( 廢中擔心係正常，你有交帶煩少d )"}]}